@Node Contents

The distribution archive should contain the following
(.info files is intentionally omitted in this listing)

Pause/bin/pause                               - The main executeable file
Pause/bin/Locale/Catalogs/dansk/Pause.catalog - danish locale file
Pause/doc/pause.guide                         - this Amigaguide file
Pause/src/pause.pas                           - Pascal sourcecode
Pause/src/paus.pas                            - Pascal unit source
Pause/src/LocaleTrans/Pause.ct                - locale translation file
Pause/src/LocaleTrans/Pause.cd                - locale translation file

@EndNode

